# --- [ üü¢ HOW TO EDIT ] ---
# 1. NO SPACES around '='! (e.g., GAME_WRAPPER="mangohud" is OK).
# 2. These settings OVERRIDE the Global defaults in your main config.
# 3. Use '#' to disable a setting and fallback to Global.
# =============================================================================

# --- [ 1. GAME WRAPPER ] ---
# Overrides: export GAME_WRAPPER (default is usually gamemoderun)
# This runs BEFORE the game executable.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# EXAMPLE: Use "Your_Option" for this specific game
GAME_WRAPPER=""

# EXAMPLE: Run without any wrapper (empty)
# GAME_WRAPPER=""


# --- [ 2. EXTRA ARGUMENTS ] ---
# Overrides: export GAME_EXTRA_ARGS
# These options are added AFTER the game executable.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# EXAMPLE: Use "Your_Argument" for this specific game
GAME_EXTRA_ARGS=""

# ‚ö†Ô∏è NOTE:
# Do not add '--' here; the system handles the execution chain.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------


# --- [ üí° FALLBACK LOGIC ] ---
# If these variables are commented out or missing, SDY will
# automatically use the Global values from your Main config file.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

